  prepFisica_activity_bum_bum_fit_title: 'Bum Bum Cuerpo Fit',
  prepFisica_activity_bum_bum_fit_desc:
    'Complete full-body workout that combines cardio, muscle toning and fat burning. Work legs, glutes, abs, arms and back in dynamic and energizing sessions. Burn calories, tone muscles, improve your fitness and transform your silhouette.',

  prepFisica_activity_yoga_flow_title: 'Yoga Flow',
  prepFisica_activity_yoga_flow_desc:
    'Dynamic yoga sequences (Vinyasa Flow) to improve flexibility, balance, inner strength and mind-body connection. Flow between asanas with conscious breathing, develop stability in inversions and improve your body alignment. Ideal for dancers seeking to center themselves and stretch deeply.',

  prepFisica_activity_dance_barre_title: 'Dance Barre',
  prepFisica_activity_dance_barre_desc:
    'Fusion of classical ballet, pilates and fitness at the barre for dancers. Barre exercises, pliés, relevés, leg and ab work to strengthen, streamline your figure and improve your dance technique. Elegance, posture and elongated muscles in the style of professional ballerinas.',

  prepFisica_activity_mate_pilates_title: 'Mat Pilates',
