  // What to Expect Section
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_title: 'What to Expect from Your Private Dance Classes?',
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_p1:
    "At Farray's International Dance Center, our private dance classes are designed to maximize your progress in the shortest time possible. Each 60-minute session is 100% personalized: your teacher dedicates full attention to correcting your technique, adapting the pace to your level, and focusing on your specific goals—whether mastering a style, preparing for a performance, or simply gaining confidence on the dance floor.",
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_p2:
    "Unlike regular group classes where the teacher must divide attention among 15-20 students, in private classes you are the sole focus. This means you'll learn 3 to 4 times faster: in a single private class you advance what would normally take 3-4 group classes. It's the most efficient way to learn to dance, especially if you have complicated schedules, ambitious goals, or simply value your time.",
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_p3:
    'Our teachers are highly qualified in over 25 dance styles: from Cuban Salsa, Bachata and Kizomba to Hip Hop, Dancehall, Contemporary and Ballet. You can choose to focus on a single style or combine several according to your interests. Additionally, we offer total flexibility: choose schedules that fit your agenda (mornings, afternoons, weekends), record your classes to review at home, and decide whether you prefer in-person classes at our Barcelona center, online via Zoom, or even at your home.',

